:"May 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, visited me while I was ill in Mecca. I said, \u201cI have some wealth. May I donate all of it?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cNo.\u201d I said, \u201cHalf of it?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cNo.\u201d I said, \u201cA third of it?\u201d The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21091,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/10\/25\/prophet-condemns-killing-children\/","url_meta":{"origin":36617,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Children: The Prophet condemns killing of children","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 25, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Aswad ibn Sari\u2019 reported: I came with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and participated in the battle with him. I engaged in the skirmish that day, until some people killed children. The Prophet was told about it and he said, \u201cWhat is wrong with these\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26690,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/07\/01\/salat-coolness-delight-eyes\/","url_meta":{"origin":36617,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet&#8217;s delight in his prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 1, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBeloved to me in the world are women and perfume, yet the delight of my eyes was made in prayer.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 3939 Grade: Qawi (strong) according to Al-Dhahabi Imam al-Munawi commented, \"His love for women\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41016,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/08\/31\/tawbah-coward\/","url_meta":{"origin":36617,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Forgiveness for acts of cowardice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 31, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"'Abdur Rahman reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cNo man says three times, \u2018I seek forgiveness from Allah, besides whom there is no God, the Living, the Sustainer, and I repent to Him,\u2019 except that he will be forgiven, even if he fled from battle.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/36617","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=36617"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"h